    "# Adjusting for overcounting\n",
    "\n",
    "Total number of unique permutations of $n$ objects that has $r_1, r_2, r_3,..., r_k$ repetitive elements is:\n",
    "$$ \\frac{n!}{r_1!r_2!...r_k!} $$"
   ]
